data.description: Located in the Heart of Graford, this home has great curb appeal. When you enter the home you will notice all of the natural light from the wall of windows giving the room a light and airy feel, this home features 4 large bedrooms, front of the house has beautiful mature shade trees and small 2 car garage with carport. Behind the 8' privacy fence you will find a beautiful backyard that would be perfect for entertaining guests. There is a  7' deep pool and wraparound deck with gazebo as well as a covered seating area off of the side of the house. Pool will need a new liner and is currently unusable.
